dc_description_s: This data layer represents school districts for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2020.[This data layer displays the geographic area of the School Districts with Polk County, Wisconsin. The data layer shares topology in the areas where survey grade PLSS corners have been collected and with existing parcels. The school district boundaries are displayed per the school district classification within the Polk County tax roll.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://www.polkcountywi.gov/government/divisions_and_departments/environmental_services_division/division_of_gis/gis_data_portal.php
